These are Puzzles for 5x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-1::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, taxi, skateboard, trike, motorbike
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, blend, fonseca, game, baccarat
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, fantasy, drama, animation, spy
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, lilac, aquamarine, green, black
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, rugby, sailing, skateboarding, skiing
 1. the person who likes black is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the game-smoker##1
 3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 6. the person who likes green is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the person who likes green is the person driving the tram##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
12. the person watching animation movies is the person who likes black##1
13. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
15. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
16. the blend-smoker is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who likes white##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3    |    4     |      5      |
| Transport      | motorbike     | tram          | taxi   | skateboard | trike    |
| Cigar          | fonseca  | pall-mall        | baccarat | blend   | game |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts   | fantasy       | animation | spy  | drama   |
| Color   | lilac  | green     | black | aquamarine  | white    |
| Sport         | sailing | skateboarding | rugby   | golf     | skiing      |

