 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes pink##1
 9. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person who likes red##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is between the tower house and the person driving the helicopter##2
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
13. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
14. the cape-cod house is the person playing backgammon##1
15. the cape-cod house is between the game-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2
16. the game-smoker is on the far right##1

