.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-14::.
There are 5 different nationalities: british, polish, turkish, chinese, argentine
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, security-guard, firefighter, fisherman
5 different games are played: domino, snooker, mah-jongg, chess, backgammon
There are 5 different favourite colors: yellow, fuchsia, ebony, pink, orange
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, handball, ice-hockey, parkour, sailing
 1. the person playing domino is on the left of the turkish##1
 2. the polish is on the right of the security-guard##1
 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 5. the firefighter is on the left of the british##1
 6. the security-guard is between the argentine and the person who's sport is handball##2
 7. the bartender is in the middle##1
 8. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
 9. the fisherman is on the far right##1
10. the security-guard is the person playing mah-jongg##1
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the british##1
12. the person playing snooker is the chinese##1
13. the fisherman is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
14. the turkish is the person who likes orange##1
15. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
16. the firefighter is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |       4       |    5     |
| Nationality          | chinese      | british    | argentine  | turkish        | polish   |
| Job         | firefighter | dancer | bartender  | security-guard | fisherman  |
| Game   | snooker       | chess       | domino  | mah-jongg          | backgammon    |
| Color           | fuchsia    | ebony       | yellow | orange         | pink      |
| Sport         | cricket   | ice-hockey   | sailing  | parkour       | handball |

