.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-15::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, dahlia, zinnia, daisy, lily
House: wooden, futuristic, art-deco, tower, colonial
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, blend, swisher, cain, bluemaster
5 different games are played: whist, chess, canasta, monopoly, domino
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the art-deco house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the left of the colonial house##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is the person playing chess##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is between the wooden house and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 8. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the art-deco house is the bluemaster-smoker##1
10. the person driving the quad-bike is the blend-smoker##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the art-deco house##1
12. the wooden house is between the art-deco house and the futuristic house##2
13. the person driving the taxi is between the person playing canasta and the swisher-smoker##2
14. the art-deco house is the person playing whist##1
15. the person who growslily is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
16. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
17. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |         3          |       4        |      5       |
| Flower           | amaryllis | lily    | daisy | zinnia | dahlia |
| House   | tower     | futuristic     | wooden          | art-deco       | colonial      |
| Cigar   | blend      | montecristo    | cain          | bluemaster        | swisher    |
| Game         | domino    | chess       | canasta             | whist       | monopoly        |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | snowmobile | motorbike          | taxi           | airplane     |

