.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-16::.
5 different games are played: go, bridge, chess, backgammon, whist
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, old-henry, swisher, vegafina, prince
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, chesssy, tulip, lily, zinnia
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, d&b, disco, pop, rock
City: colone, venice, prague, boston, paris
 1. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to colone and the person playing go##2
 2. the fan of pop is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 3. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
 4. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the fan of disco is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the swisher-smoker is between the person traveling to venice and the person playing go##2
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
 8. the fan of country is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
10. the person playing chess is the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the left of the fan of rock##1
13. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
14. the person who growschesssy is in the middle##1
15. the fan of country is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |      5       |
| Game      | chess   | bridge        | go    | backgammon  | whist       |
| Cigar          | vegafina    | swisher       | aristoff | prince | old-henry         |
