.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-17::.
City: liverpool, san-francisco, london, new-york, paris
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bolivar, bongani, siglo, prince
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, fanta, milk, lemonade
There are 5 different nationalities: british, colombian, spanish, french, japanese
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, skiing, volleyball
 1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 3. the person traveling to london is on the left of the british##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the french##1
 5. the prince-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the spanish is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's sport is golf is the spanish##1
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
11. the french is on the right of the colombian##1
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
14. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person who's sport is baseball and the french##2
15. the dunhill-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| City          | san-francisco     | paris | liverpool  | london   | new-york     |
| Cigar         | bolivar    | bongani    | prince | dunhill  | siglo  |
| Beverage   | juice    | lemonade       | fanta   | milk     | hot-chocolate     |
| Nationality           | colombian       | french   | spanish    | japanese    | british       |
| Sport         | volleyball | skiing     | golf    | baseball | basketball |

