.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: black, emerald, amber, light-blue, fuchsia
There 5 different types of food: pepper, apple, cranberry, lime, pumpkin
5 different pets are kept: dog, fish, hamster, horse, pony
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, almond-milk, milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, siglo, old-henry, vegafina
 1. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 2. the old-henry-smoker is between the chaman-smoker and the person who likes black##2
 3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is the person who likes light-blue##1
 8. the person eating pepper is the owner of the horse##1
 9. the person who likes emerald is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the fish##2
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
12. the person eating lime is the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
14. the owner of the fish is between the person drinking milk and the owner of the horse##2
15. the person who likes light-blue is between the owner of the hamster and the person who likes emerald##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Color         | amber    | light-blue | emerald    | fuchsia   | black     |
| Food   | pumpkin       | lime       | pepper | apple    | cranberry       |
| Pet           | hamster    | fish        | horse      | dog       | pony       |
| Beverage         | milk | fanta     | hot-chocolate     | sprite  | almond-milk |
| Cigar     | havana | siglo     | chaman        | old-henry | vegafina       |

