The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, designer, doctor, librarian, dressmaker
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, subway, taxi, car
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, rowing, skiing, weightlifting
 1. the person who growspinkade is on the far left##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 3. the doctor is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the bike is between the person who's sport is rowing and the person driving the taxi##2
 5. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 7. the person who likes black is on the right of the designer##1
 8. the person who likes coral is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the librarian##1
10. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
12. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
13. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
14. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
15. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |      4      |       5       |
