.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, sprite
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, marigold, poppy, iris
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, february, may, december, july
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, bird, goat, rat, cat
There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lavender, purple, mauve, green
 1. the owner of the bird is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the owner of the goat is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who likes green##2
 6. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is the person who growsiris##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who likes lavender##2
12. the person who growsmarigold is the person who likes green##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
14. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
15. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
16. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk | 7up         | sprite    | hot-chocolate |
| Flower          | poppy   | marigold        | iris | aconite | daisy    |
| Birthday         | march   | february      | july   | december   | may   |
| Pet   | rat      | cat    | goat      | bird   | rabbit  |
| Color   | mauve     | green        | aquamarine     | lavender     | purple        |

 